Who’s your “see you at FES?” person? 👩‍❤️‍👩💙

Coffee raves started in Amsterdam as a way to bring people together—through music, movement, and caffeine instead of alcohol. A sober social space, but still full of energy, connection, and chaos (the good kind). ☕️🎶

And honestly? FES in Gurgaon is the only place I’ve seen actually get it right.

For someone like me—who loves meeting people, dancing it out, and sipping on something strong (read: matcha)—this is the scene.
It’s fun, it’s fresh, and it’s exactly the kind of community vibe I’ve been craving.
